    <item>
      <title>邱：未来两年人工智能需求将日益重要</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-26/demand-for-ai-increasingly-important-in-next-2-yrs-qiu-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[AllianceBernstein 主题创新股票首席投资官 Lei Qiu 表示，虽然人工智能超大规模企业的资本支出将在 2025 年继续增加，但增幅将取决于需求的强度。她在《彭博市场》节目中接受了彭博社 Paul Sweeney 和 Alix Steel 的采访。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-26/demand-for-ai-increasingly-important-in-next-2-yrs-qiu-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Dec 2024 17:43:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
